# Keep the build context tiny: the venv alone is ~2 GB, and the Dockerfile
# copies an explicit file list anyway -- this exists so `COPY` never waits on
# gigabytes of context upload.
venv/
.git/
.claude/
.pytest_cache/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Never bake secrets or the developer's live database into an image.
.env
system_metrics.db*

# Training/analysis artifacts -- the shipped GBT needs none of these.
*.parquet
SecIDS-CNN.h5
train_flow_model.py
scripts/
docs/
tests/

# Captures. The two demo seed pcaps are NOT ignored -- the entrypoint replays
# BOTH to populate the first-boot demo (demo-public-ips.pcap, 22 KB, benign +
# geo spread; dos-volumetric.pcap, 185 KB, the in-scope attack traffic that
# makes the feed show suspicious detections with ATT&CK badges). Only the
# unused heartbleed excerpt stays out of the image.
samples/heartbleed-excerpt.pcap

*.md
LICENSE
